metadata.name: 1.   My pet😇🤍
metadata.description:
E.S.As (Emotional Support Animals) provide support and comfort that helps us deal with challenges that might otherwise compromise our quality of life..
     Many people don’t know that owning a pet might help ease one’s anxiety and depression or give them a focus in life and so i have created this collection to create awareness and to show support to everyone going through mental health disorder🥰🤍
   Not until we are lost do we begin to understand ourselves..
          -Henry David Thorean
